---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About"
  description="About Anshuman Singh — developer and independent researcher across software engineering, AI, physics, and mathematics."
>
  <Header />

  <main id="main-content" class="mx-auto max-w-2xl px-6 py-16">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-serif font-semibold">About</h1>

    <div class="mt-6 prose prose-invert max-w-none">
      <p>
        I'm Anshuman Singh, a self-taught developer working primarily across Python, full-stack
        web development, and applied AI/ML — alongside an ongoing personal interest in physics
        and mathematics. This site is a running record of that work: what I've built, what I've
        struggled with, and what I've actually learned rather than what I merely skimmed.
      </p>
      <p>
        Most of what I write about falls into a few buckets: backend and full-stack engineering
        (Python, Flask, APIs, databases), experiments and small research notes in physics and
        math that I find genuinely interesting, notes from projects as I build them, and honest
        reflections on what a given tool, book, or course did or didn't teach me.
      </p>
      <p>
        I don't treat this journal as a highlight reel. Build logs include the parts that failed.
        Research notes include the limitations of whatever small experiment prompted them. The
        goal is a record I can actually trust later, not a portfolio optimized to impress on
        first read.
      </p>
      <h2>Elsewhere</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="https://github.com/anshuman365" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub — github.com/anshuman365</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://anshuman365.github.io" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Portfolio — anshuman365.github.io</a></li>
        <li>
          LinkedIn —
          <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/anshuman-singh-662183303/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
            linkedin.com/in/anshuman-singh-662183303/
          </a>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>
